snippet.title: Capcom Arcade Stadium – Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Relive the glory of the arcades with Capcom Arcade Stadium, a digital collection of 32 classic titles coming February 2021! The collection will be free to download with 1943 - The Battle of Midway - included, with additional games available for purchase. 

https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/capcom-arcade-stadium-switch/
